title: Holi Ayee Re
subTitle: Taking advantage of her trusting nature, an unprincipled man seduces a village maiden, only to desert her in her time of need.

title: Numbri Aadmi
subTitle: Shankar, a noble thief, attempts to kill Rana, his father's murderer, in a bid to seek revenge. However, Rana has powerful friends who stand in Shankar's way.

title: Ghar Ka Chiraag
subTitle: Kiran marries Kumar, believing her love, Ravi, to be dead. When Ravi returns years later, Kiran is forced to confront the painful secrets surrounding her past and her marriage.

title: Meet Mere Man Ke
subTitle: Thakur Jagat Pratap Singh, a man from high society, falls in love with a courtesan, Jyoti, after she saves his life. However, the gulf in social status of the two prevents them from being together.

title: Aa Gale Lag Jaa
subTitle: Roshni, a wealthy heiress, wants to marry Suraj, a poor man, but her mother disapproves as his father is an ex-prisoner. Meanwhile, a series of murders take place and the suspicion falls on Suraj.

title: Bade Ghar Ki Beti
subTitle: Mala, a poor girl, marries the son of her father's employer. Things, however, take a turn for the worse when her father-in-law dies and his ruthless children show their true colours.

title: Suhana Safar
subTitle: Enticed by his poetry, Sapna travels to India from the US to meet the poet Ujjwala. There, she meets a man, Sunil, who falls for her but he decides to help her meet Ujjwala.

title: Chhoti Si Baat
subTitle: Arun, a timorous man, falls for Prabha but is reluctant to express his feelings. However, things take a turn when Nagesh attempts to woo Prabha.

title: Zakhm
subTitle: A boy, born into a family of varying religions, finds himself embroiled in communal riots. Soon, his mother's death becomes an issue raised to fulfil political agendas.

title: Param Dharam
subTitle: Savitri believes that her illegitimate child with her deceased lover, Vijay, was stillborn and did not survive. Years later, Savitri's world changes when she learns that her firstborn is alive.

title: Mehndi
subTitle: Newly-wed Pooja is left shocked when her in-laws and her husband start ill-treating her. Unable to bear the mistreatment, she decides to teach them a lesson.

title: Aadmi
subTitle: Vijay, a factory supervisor, is falsely accused and arrested for killing his family. Just when he is at his lowest point, an inspector offers to help him in return for capturing the son of a gangster.

subTitle: Under her brother's influence, Laxmi mistreats her stepchildren, causing them to run away from home. His intentions are revealed when he throws her and her husband out of the house, destitute.

title: Patthar Ke Phool
subTitle: Suraj falls in love with Kiran but does not know that she is the daughter of an underworld kingpin. Suraj's life takes a drastic turn when the same criminal kills his father.

title: Mangani
subTitle: Due to her appearance, a woman faces persistent challenges. Subjected to constant ridicule, she is rejected by numerous men, including her college crush.
